``The institutional detachment of accounting standard setting from banking regulation'' (M\"ugge and Perry, 2014, p. 206)  \#\#\#
\par
``The IASB and FASB are important champions of equilibrium finance, the principles of which are embedded in their overarching conceptual frameworks.'' (M\"ugge and Perry, 2014, p. 207)
